text: Siavash Shafizadeh (born 30 March 1944) is an Iranian wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman bantamweight at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:Iranian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Iran Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
